{% block content %}
<div class="location__conference-centre">
    <div class="hero hero--short">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <h1>The venue</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">The Walker Theatre, Theatre Severn, Shrewsbury</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="conference-centre">
        <div class="map page">
            <div class="conference-centre-info">
                <div id="directionsPanel"></div>
                <img src="{{ "theatre-severn-tmp.jpg" | asset_url }}" alt="theatre-severn" />
                <div class="vcard">
                    <div class="fn org">The Walker Theatre</div>
                    <div class="adr">
                        <div class="street-address">
                            <span>Theatre Severn</span>
                            <span>Frankwell Quay</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="locality">Shrewsbury</span>
                         <span class="region">Shropshire</span>
                         <div class="postal-code">SY3 8FT</div>
                         <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/dir//Theatre+Severn,+Frankwell+Quay,+Shrewsbury+SY3+8FT,+United+Kingdom/@52.710636,-2.757613,15z/data=!4m12!1m3!3m2!1s0x0:0x2db80e864a447bcf!2sTheatre+Severn!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x487a9e5703dd4521:0x2db80e864a447bcf!2m2!1d-2.757613!2d52.710636" target="_blank">Get directions</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="map-canvas" class="map-canvas">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="conference-centre--grid-row">
                <div class="conference-centre--grid-unit">
                    <p>Theatre Severn was officially opened on 25 March 2009 and is situated on Frankwell Quay, a stunning riverside location and one of the main gateways into the town.</p>
                    <p>**REPLACE: The only purpose-built auditorium in Shropshire, it shares a large site with the Royal Shrewsbury Hospital, making it easy to find, with dedicated, private parking and great public transport links.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="conference-centre--grid-unit">
                    <h2 class="tertiary-heading">Arriving by public transport</h2>
                    <p>If you arrive in Shrewsbury by train, the theatre is just a 10 minute walk along the riverside.</p>
                    <p><a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/dir//Theatre+Severn,+Frankwell+Quay,+Shrewsbury+SY3+8FT,+United+Kingdom/@52.710636,-2.757613,15z/data=!4m12!1m3!3m2!1s0x0:0x2db80e864a447bcf!2sTheatre+Severn!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x487a9e5703dd4521:0x2db80e864a447bcf!2m2!1d-2.757613!2d52.710636" target="_blank">Directions</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
